data.description: Welcome to the charming 207 East McGee! Conveniently located near Bass Pro Shops and just a short drive to Missouri State. This darling home has been well cared for and wonderfully updated and it is ready for its new owners. Offering 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, 1 car garage with 834 square finished square footage. The front porch is great for a morning coffee. Inside you will find hardwood floors, a good-sized living space, a kitchen-dining combo, and a finished mudroom that sits just off the garage. The backyard has a patio for entertaining and a large yard space. This home is not going to last long, so do't miss out!
